---
// Replace the bio copy and headshot below.
---

<section id="about" class="section">
  <div class="container about">
    <div class="about__photo">
      <img src="/images/personal.jpg" alt="Portrait of Mehrdad Majzoobi" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
    <div class="about__text">
      <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
      <h2>A bit about me</h2>
      <p class="lead">
          I am explorer and risk taker at heart. I believe life is too short
          to play it safe. I am highly curious and constantly learning new things. 
      </p>
      <p>
        I am facinated by the promise of agentic systems these days and that's where I am 
        spending most of my time, beside contributing to open source projects and coding. 
        If you are an AI researcher, specially working on RL & agents, 
        I would love to connect and collaborate. 
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    display: grid;
    gap: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    align-items: start;
  }
  @media (min-width: 760px) {
    .about {
      grid-template-columns: 4fr 7fr;
    }
  }
  .about__photo img {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--hairline);
    background: var(--surface);
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
    object-fit: cover;
  }
</style>
